    <item>
      <title>诺特警告称，如果对金融监管的关注度减弱，经济将陷入自由落体</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/knot-warns-of-economies-in-free-fall-if-focus-on-financial-regulation-wanes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最有权力的金融监管机构主席警告政客们，如果他们优先考虑其他公共政策领域而不是保护金融体系，他们可能会把大部分时间花在“为自由落体的经济制定救援计划”上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/knot-warns-of-economies-in-free-fall-if-focus-on-financial-regulation-wanes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 13:05:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
